    "mission": "Ectropy exists to transform construction into a transparent, efficient, and sustainable industry — providing the world's first federated construction platform where every stakeholder can collaborate seamlessly while maintaining their preferred tools and workflows.",
    "vision": "Democratize construction technology through open-source infrastructure, enabling community-driven innovation and creating sustainable value for every contributor to the built environment.",
