      "name": "BOX — BIM + BOM + VOX Spatial Decision Container",
      "category": "data-platform",
      "description": "The fundamental unit of construction intelligence. Convergence of BIM geometry, BOM materials, and VOX spatial decision surface into a single addressable 3D cell. Three resolution tiers: COARSE (100mm), STANDARD (40mm), FINE (10mm). Parent-child hierarchy with PostGIS spatial index. Canonical schema defined in BOX-ARCHITECTURE-2026-03-26.docx.",
